Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm gonna teach you a thing or two about being a dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:08.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So, listen up, my boy, because I'm only gonna say this once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Look at this castle where you live
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's pretty sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:16.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can't be a dragon here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Uh, I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Look at these books up on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just finished organizing those!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:24.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This treasure pile's not right, I fear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Trust me, I got you covered here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:30.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You see all this soft pony stuff you're surrounded with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This has got to be the first thing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Nothin' 'bout this place says "dragon den"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:36.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's too much fluff
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All these fancy robes, toss in a pile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:43.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Take those goblets, dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is that gold? Still not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:49.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,De-ponifying might just take a while
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sure, this place is grandiose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But to a dragon, it's just gross
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:59.07,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Time we make the lot all disappear~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Reality you need a dose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To all these ponies, you're too close
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You just can't be a dragon here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Good job, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:10.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But this is still just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:14.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Each and every dragon has a swagger all his own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:18.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Watch and I'll show you what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:23.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can't move like this with so much stuff to weigh you down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A dragon always keeps it lean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Lose this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:30.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ooh, this is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:33.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your life is soft, your scales are coiffed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These pillows, beds, and sheets are washed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:39.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A delight, but it's just not right what's underneath~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Every dragon must be free
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Look at you then look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:47.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Since when do dragons brush their teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ha! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sure, this place is grandiose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But to a dragon, it's just gross
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Time we make the lot all disappear~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:57.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just grab it all and give to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After that, then you'll be free
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:05.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You just can't be a dragon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:06.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I feel better already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,See? What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You're very lucky that I found you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now, go get me some more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:13.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:17.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get you all the cushy pony stuff I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:18.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Great! Go get 'em... son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:26.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause this dragon just can't wait to live here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,[sinister_laughter]